base of 2
          1 0 1 1
position  3 2 1 0
          | | | |
          | | | |----> 2^0 * 1   = 1 * 1  = 1
          | | |---> 2^1 * 1  =  2 * 1  = 2
          | |--> 2^2 * 0  = 4 * 0  = 0
          |-> 2^3 * 1  = 8 * 1  = 8

  = 8 + 0 + 2 + 1 = 11

Binary number -> base 2
             1 1 0 0 1 1 0 1
position     7 6 5 4 3 2 1 0
             | | | | | | | |
             | | | | | | | |--> 2^0 * 1 = 1 * 1 = 1
             | | | | | | |--> 2^1 * 0 = 2 * 0 = 0
             | | | | | |--> 2^2 * 1 = 4 * 1 = 4
             | | | | |--> 2^3 * 1 = 8 * 1 = 8
             | | | |--> 2^4 * 0 = 16 * 0 = 0
             | | |--> 2^5 * 0 = 32 * 0 = 0
             | |--> 2^6 * 1 = 64 * 1 = 64
             |--> 2^7 * 1 = 128 * 1 = 128

Total = 128 + 64 + 8 + 4 + 1 = 205


Octal numbering system -> Base 8 (0 to 7)
An Octal number 567 to convert to decimal number

           5 6 7
Position   2 1 0
           | | |
           | | |----> 8^0 * 7  = 1 * 7  = 7
           | |---> 8^1 * 6  = 8 * 6  = 48
           |--> 8^2 * 5  = 64 * 5  = 320

Total = 320 + 48 + 7 = 375


 Hexadecimal number: 0 to 9, A to F (0 to 15) Base 16
 A = 10, B = 11, C = 12, D = 13, E = 14, F = 15

              A F 3 D
  Position    3 2 1 0
              | | | |---------> 16 ^ 0 * 13 = 1 * 13 = 13
              | | |--------> 16 ^ 1 * 3 = 16 * 3 = 48
              | |----> 16 ^ 2 * 15 = 256 * 15 = 3840
              |----> 16 ^ 3 * 10 = 4096 * 10 = 40960

Total = 40960 + 3840 + 48 + 13 = 44861


