Converting Octal to Binary
Base 8 : 1707  -> 001 111 000 111 = 0000 0011 1100 0111
Base 8 : 163   -> 001 110 011 = 0111 0011

Converting Binary to Octal
Base 2: 1011 1101 -> 010 111 101  = 275 base of 8
Base 2: 0101 1010 1100 0011 -> 000 101 101 011 000 011 = 55303 base of 8

   Hexadecimal     Binary mapping        Hexadecimal      Binary Mapping
       0              0000                   8               1000
       1              0001                   9               1001
       2              0010                   A               1010
       3              0011                   B               1011
       4              0100                   C               1100
       5              0101                   D               1101
       6              0110                   E               1110
       7              0111                   F               1111

Hexa to binary
Base 16: 0x3C7 -> 0000 0011 1100 0111
Base 16: 0xABCD -> 1010 1011 1100 1101

Binary to Hexa
Base 2: 0001 1110 0011 0110 -> 0x1E36
Base 2: 1011 1101 -> 0xBD


